&gt;My purpose is not to discourage elaborate ritual=\r\ns. Do them if there is social pressure to do so or you find them interestin=\r\ng. But, atleast ensure that mantropadesa happens peacefully and correctly. =\r\nMore importantly, ensure that the young man does some sadhana with Gayatri =\r\nmantra everyday, after upanayanam.&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;Also, it is perfectly acceptable=\r\n (and beneficial) to initiate the young person into homam after upanayanam =\r\nis done. On the same day or a few days later, one can teach a simple versio=\r\nn of Ganapathi homam and let the young person perform it by oneself during =\r\nweekends or so. One can start off with the super-short procedure and slowly=\r\n add things. Doing Gayatri mantra everyday and homam now and then will acce=\r\nlerate the spiritual evolution of the young person.&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;Best regards,&lt;b=\r\nr&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;----------------------------------------------------------&lt;b=\r\nr&gt;Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;br&gt;&quot;D=\r\no It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;=\r\na href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://www.Ved=\r\nicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Films that make a difference: &lt;a href=3D&quot;http://sar=\r\naswatifilms.org/&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://SaraswatiFilms.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Spirit=\r\nuality: &lt;a href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&quot; target=3D&quot;_b=\r\nlank&quot;&gt;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;\nJyotish writings: =\r\n&lt;a href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot;=\r\n&gt;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;---------------------=\r\n-------------------------------------&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;---- Sunitha &lt;&lt;a href=3D&quot;ma=\r\nilto:sunitha_macherla%40yahoo.com